WEBVTT

00:02.778 --> 00:08.561
In Italy, navy and coast guard ships pick up about 1,500 migrants in 24 hours,...

00:08.701 --> 00:11.715
...most fleeing war and poverty in African regions.

00:12.339 --> 00:15.629
In Israel, Israeli prime minister Benjamin Netanyahu...

00:15.930 --> 00:18.843
...voices his disapproval of the recent Iran Agreement.

00:20.678 --> 00:25.833
In India, Prime Minister Narendra Modi announces a National Air Quality Index Monday...

00:26.257 --> 00:29.195
...to keep track of pollution levels in ten of its cities.

00:32.463 --> 00:36.196
In an unprecedented move, China says it helped ten countries...

00:36.274 --> 00:39.952
...evacuate 225 of their citizens from Yemen.

00:41.854 --> 00:44.894
And finally from Switzerland, after a two-year hiatus...

00:45.192 --> 00:47.991
...scientists at the European Center for Nuclear Research...

00:48.258 --> 00:50.901
...restart their "Big Bang" Large Hadron Collider.

